
~BM*** Friend ***

~FTUsage:~RS friend add / delete  <friend id[@<server>]> [<friend id..> ...]

Every user has a friends list which gives information on when the given
friend is logged on and in what group. Use this command to add or delete
a friend(s) from the list. Friends can be local or on immediately connected
servers.

~FYSee also:~RS lsfriends, ftell, femote

